Body elongate, roughly cylindrical close to head and gradually more compressed towards caudal fin. Dorsal and ventral profiles of trunk slightly convex. Dorsal and ventral profiles of caudal peduncle straight (
Fig. 2
). Integument thick, especially over base of pectoral and caudal fins. Small papillae on lips, and scattered on dorsal surface of head.

